_json.gridTitle: Hogben Mugs - Forget-me-not - eau de nil
_json.description: Another new design from this beautiful range. Little forget-me-not flowers available in six gentle colours: eau de nil, yellow, grey, blue, cream and pink. Hogben Pottery specialise in a technique known as sprigging (applying separately moulded designs in 3D). Attaching these to a range of jugs, bowls and mugs, which are then hand painted by Jane and her team.
